 &HT;    How conferences will look in the next century
 &HT;    By Tony Barnhart
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ACC:
</P>
<P>
   NORTH
</P>
<P>
   Boston College
</P>
<P>
   Maryland
</P>
