</P>
<P>
   _ Outlook: In his first season, Gailey faces no easy task. His
four-wideout sets and disciplined manner have excited some players,
but not everyone has bought in to the whole package. It's still an
aging team with a dwindling talent base, particularly on offense.
At times in camp, star running back Emmitt Smith appeared spent.
Troy Aikman remains the quarterback and Michael Irvin the main
target. The defense looks soft on the edges of the front seven, but
it should be fairly solid, especially the secondary, even with
nagging injuries to Deion Sanders.
</P>
<P>
   ARIZONA CARDINALS
</P>
