<TEXT>
<P>
   SAN FRANCISCO 49ERS
</P>
<P>
   _ Coach: Steve Mariucci is 14-4 in one season with the 49ers.
</P>
<P>
   _ Last season: 13-3, first in NFC West (lost in NFC championship
game).
</P>
