</P>
<P>
   BOOKS-NOTES _ Book Notes. John Lewis' memoir, ``Walking with the
Wind'' and Dorothy Allison's novel, ``Cave Dweller,'' are among the
nominees for the Lillian Smith Book Awards. Also, Florida author
James W. Hall introduces a new mystery series with a female sleuth
and Pocket Books taps into web surfers with a trilogy about love in
cyberspace. (O'Briant, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
