<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19980902.0182 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-02 14:44 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5145 &Cx1f; tad-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HAITI-GROOVE-0903-COX     09-02 0563
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HAITI-GROOVE-0903-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    OUTRAGE ERUPTS OVER 'STEREOTYPICAL' REMARK IN POPULAR SUMMER
MOVIE
 &HT;    Moving in both the (i) International and (l) Lifestyle
categories.
 &HT;    By SHELLEY EMLING 
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service 
<TEXT>
