</P>
<P>
   CORPUS-THEATER (New York) _ The Manhattan Theater Club prepares
to stage the controversial play ``Corpus Christi.'' By Robin
Pogrebin.
</P>
<P>
   ROME-CONCERT-HALL (Rome) _ Arts Abroad: Renzo Piano designs a
new concert hall complex in Rome. By John Tagliabue.
</P>
<P>
   COUNTERCULTURE-BOOK-REVIEW (Undated) _ ``Steal This Dream: Abbie
Hoffman and the Countercultural Revolution in America,'' by Larry
Sloman (Doubleday).
</P>
<P>
