   DOW-MAIN _ Major U.S. market averages got out to a surprisingly
robust start in Wednesday's trading session. The Dow Jones
Industrial Average is up 48 points and the Nasdaq 20 points.
(Walker, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
