</P>
<P>
   FBN-DOLPHINS-STUBBS _ DAVIE, Fla. _ Stubbs, the Dolphins'
veteran defensive end, has prospered most when he's played on a
defense that's terrorized running backs who dared turn the corner.
Stubbs was a staple on the legendary University of Miami teams that
chased down and pulverized ballcarriers. And his best season in the
NFL was when he started 15 games for the Cowboys, whose defense
followed the Hurricanes' blueprint. Now, Stubbs feels he's back on
a football freeway, with no speed limit. (D'Angelo, Palm Beach
Post) MOVED.
</P>
