<HEADER>
A5828 &Cx1f; tad-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BRAIN-SIDE-life-COX     09-02 0588
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BRAIN-SIDE-life-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;    
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Automobile accidents account for 50% of brain injuries
 &HT;    By Ellen Lee
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
