   (NYT9) BEL AIR, Calif. -- Sept. 2, 1998 --
SWIMMING-POOL-DESIGN-1, 9-2 -- What do owners want? A pool
disguised as a pond, large enough to do laps, in a
Tarzan-meets-Jane setting. Rose Tarlow's ``natural'' pool and
pavilion in Bel Air took a herculean effort. (Tim Street-Porter/New
York Times Photo) LITE
</P>
